# SIGNATURE COMBAT MOVES
*Reference to combat mechanics documentation*

## Overview
Signature combat moves are personalized techniques developed by experienced warriors.

## Creating Signature Moves
See [Combat Techniques](techniques_mechanics.md) for the complete technique system.

Signature moves combine existing techniques with character flavor and reduced Flow cost.

**Guidelines:**
- Based on existing combat techniques
- Cost 1 less Flow than base technique (minimum 0)
- Unique narrative description
- Earned at moderate milestones

